Experimenting with easier ways to make patches~

 Here I used 3 ways:
1. Iron on sheets on felt cloth
2. Iron on (photoshoped with texture) on felt cloth
3. Iron on sheeys on felt cloth then sewed over.

 I really like the effect of sewing over iron on, this way I don't really need
to sew very detailed stuff because there is already color below it. Yet, it
still has the embroidered effect.

Turn Foam to Metal Easy Alchemy 
把泡沫板變成鐵片〜

 Want to learn how to turn Foam to Metal? haha Learn to paint Foam to look like
metal. This is a cool hack I learn before from a Prop Maker for a TV Studio
before.
想把泡沫板變成鐵片嗎？哈哈看起來像鐵片啦~這是一個很簡單的小技巧~

 When to use this method: If you live in a house where you can’t use spray paint
or primer (Landlord will kill me if I get paint on the floors LOL) or you don’t
have a lot of time.~
什麼時候可以用這個技巧呢？要是你的家不能用噴漆（房東會生氣哈哈）或是你沒時間了~

 Materials:
Foam Sheets 泡沫板
Acrylic Paint (Black, Silver and Brown) 亞克力 （黑，銀，咖啡）
Glue 白膠水
Paint Brush (1 small and 1 big ) 刷子 （ 一大， 一小）
Sponge Brush or Sponge 海綿

 Est. Time: Depends on the size of your project， 看project的大小

 Difficulty: 2/10
